OL,3,CGuernsey politician, Deputy Peter
OL,4,CRoffey, to stand down at 2025 election
OL,6,FOne of longest-serving politicians,
OL,7,FDeputy Peter Roffey, has announced
OL,8,Fhe'll stand down at the next election.
OL,10,FPeter Roffey is currently President of
OL,11,Fthe Committee for Employment & Social
OL,12,FSecurity and the States' Trading
OL,13,FSupervisory Board.
OL,15,FIn a statement this morning (Monday 27
OL,16,FMay) Mr Roffey said: "After
OL,17,Fsignificant reflection, I have decided
OL,18,Fnot to stand in the 2025 general
OL,19,Felection.
