OL,4,CRoffey, to stand down at 2025 election
OL,6,FAdding more about his decision he
OL,7,Fsaid: "After that, I feel that I will
OL,8,Fhave well and truly done my current
OL,9,Ftour of duty as a deputy.
OL,11,F"This feeling is strengthened
OL,12,Fconsiderably by the fact that since re-
OL,13,F joining the States in 2016 I have
OL,14,Fsuffered a major bereavement, losing
OL,15,Fthe person who defined my life.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
