OL,3,CGuernsey politician, Deputy Peter
OL,4,CRoffey, to stand down at 2025 election
OL,6,F"In retrospect taking on a massive
OL,7,Fworkload straight after that loss
OL,8,Fmeant I never really gave myself the
OL,9,Ftime or space to fully adjust to new
OL,10,Frealities. I now intend to give myself
OL,11,Fthat space.
OL,13,F"If being a deputy was the sort of job
OL,14,Fwhere you could take a year's
OL,15,Fsabbatical would be my ideal choice.
OL,16,FBut it is not. So, with more than a
OL,17,Ftinge of sadness, I have decided to
OL,18,Fsimply step down from the States
OL,19,Finstead.
