OL,3,CGuernsey politician, Deputy Peter
OL,4,CRoffey, to stand down at 2025 election
OL,6,F"Although I certainly don't rule out
OL,7,Fstanding for public office again in
OL,8,Fthe future.
OL,10,F"After I have left the assembly I will
OL,11,Fcontinue to follow Guernsey politics
OL,12,Fwith great interest and wish the class
OL,13,Fof 2025 every success in facing the
OL,14,Fsignificant challenges which lie
OL,15,Fahead."
